data.description: Indulge in the epitome of luxury living with this single owner Bloomfield Wisteria floorplan home showcasing meticulous craftsmanship, this residence offers both elegance and functionality. The gourmet kitchen, a chef's delight, features a gas cooktop, double oven, and granite countertops. As you step inside, hand-scraped hardwood floors guide you through the open layout. The home includes a dedicated office and a media room, complementing the 4 large bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms. Outdoors, discover a resort-style oasis with a pool boasting a waterfall and slide—an entertainer's paradise. Beyond the property, the neighborhood provides miles of walking trails, four community pools, two fitness centers, and four clubhouses. Adding to the community allure, the HOA sponsors numerous events throughout the year, fostering a sense of connection among neighbors. This vibrant neighborhood spirit sets the stage for a truly exceptional living experience.
